                                <h2 class="text-h-mort">What can you expect during your initial consultation?</h2>
                                <span>If you are considering hair restoration in Houston, Texas, an appointment can be made with Dr. Danielle Andry or Dr. Nandi Wijay . You can expect the initial consultation to last an hour or more. In your consultation, your surgeon will:</span>
                                <div class="performed-clickbox">
                                    <a class="breast-click" href="/contact-us">book a consult</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6 no-padding service-left-cta">
